ike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T11:49:43.000Z","msg":"拜託唔好咁on9<br />\n支票有效期一年,麻煩你計下個日期先再決定,唔好on99比人恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ca4cf2017cc34515149352eb2da7ad9181b8ae","tid":605060,"uid":175969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T12:04:49.000Z","msg":"最佳解答<br />\n有效期開票日起計六個月, 但收票人有權向你追討未經過數的支票, 取過期的支票要求閣下更改日期簽名証實再過數, 因為你根本還未清還他公司/私人的數, 如果他公司/私人遣失你的支票, 你要他們付銀行停止支付費用, 確定這支票未經過戶, 後才發另外一張新支票給他們. <br />\n延長有效期 - 可以你簽名更改日期便可以再多六個月(不建議太長), 因為你容易遣忘戶口存款是否足夠, 當這票突然過數會無錢給付.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.answers.yahoo.com/question/index?qid=20071115000051KK02151\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.answers.yahoo.com%2Fquestion%2Findex%3Fqid%3D20071115000051KK02151&d=pA7LzFYulaAqKx0ipF9zeb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=20543d56\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.answers.yahoo.com/question/index?qid=20071115000051KK02151</a>"},{"pid":"651d8ae024b8a865a542da98234629998d4d915b","tid":605060,"uid":37447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c494a6a9768a0b94e5527da61d839e0db28f3013","tid":605060,"uid":174757,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T11:49:43.000Z","msg":"拜託唔好咁on9<br />\n支票有效期一年,麻煩你計下個日期先再決定,唔好on99比人恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T15:17:33.000Z","msg":"其實呢，你柒左一次就算啦<br />\n<br />\n柒完一次仲要衝出黎柒多鑊<br />\n<br />\n你老豆當初射你落廁所都冇咁嬲"},{"pid":"0ecb8905739503a9df1cc02bcdae8eb68abc7aac","tid":605060,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cdad816e82ee3d9fc1ed62cb4b9a0346f902ded","tid":605060,"uid":174757,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"5df112964cc30d3fe850306f9e8eb3afb5de6e70","tid":605060,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T10:08:26.000Z","msg":"係房屋處比我...張票17年8月3日出....唉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T10:09:32.000Z","msg":"你有冇腦架?唔通開張2047比你?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime"